summary:
I started my career at Shell in The Hague and London. Completed an MBA at INSEAD and moved to Singapore in 2003 where I lived for 18 years, starting several companies as well as an investment fund focused on rapidly scaling B2B technology companies. Moved with the family to the Netherlands in 2021 and looking at ways to use my experience in a new environment.

I have been trained as an executive coach and enjoy working with teams to help them become more effective. 

Feel free to connect with me but please provide some context as I prefer to connect with people who do so.
